  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1028">
<l>kuṭiceyvārk killai paruva maṭiceytu </l>
<l>māṉaṅ karutak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a family suffers by (one's) indolence and false dignity there is to be so season (good or bad) to those who strive to raise their family.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
